description.en: The main goal of the project is an informal association, communication of traders and developers from all over the world. The DGLCOIN project will provide for this purpose an island located in Europe, which will be the main base for meetings and events related to cryptocurrency. Paying great attention to the ecology of the planet, mining farms will be based on the island, with a power source from solar panels.
